{"tid":1050588,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【食炸雞洗腦】KFC染紅無咗上校！ 變身雷鋒主題餐廳有幾癲？","createTime":"2019-03-07T03:35:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-07T14:43:08.000Z","uid":39464,"like":2,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"857a9df8a005bcdaf4b7b582f4b11e813a97023a","tid":1050588,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T03:35:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190306/large/1551868099_42cd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190306%2Flarge%2F1551868099_42cd.jpg&h=38afd688&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190306/large/1551881789_0ec9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190306%2Flarge%2F1551881789_0ec9.jpg&h=87ccc608&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190306/large/1551868274_bd75.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190306%2Flarge%2F1551868274_bd75.jpg&h=8ead50ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190306/large/1551881856_fb0e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190306%2Flarge%2F1551881856_fb0e.jpg&h=784f37df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n邊吃美式炸雞，邊看着中共紅色偶像雷鋒，會有甚麼感受？肯德基（KFC）於周日（3日）在湖南長沙望城開了全國首間「雷鋒主題餐廳」，讓這個共產黨樣板人物正式「進駐」美式餐廳。事件連美國傳媒都有報道，形容餐廳出現美國招牌與中共紅色偶像是「罕見搭配」。<br />\n<br />\n湖南長沙市望城縣是雷鋒的故鄉。這別樹一格的KFC分店被改頭換面，透明玻璃貼滿卡通版雷鋒貼紙，店門口擺放身穿綠衣、頭戴軍帽的「雷小鋒」與「雷風俠」公仔。點餐櫃枱及用餐區，亦貼滿各式口號及標語，例如「雷鋒家鄉學雷鋒」，還有「雷鋒七問」，以及他生前笑得開懷的照片等。餐廳更播放着雷鋒詩歌《南來的燕子》，疑是要對顧客洗腦式灌輸「雷鋒精神」。相反，KFC創辦人桑德斯上校淪為了大配角。<br />\n<br />\n肯德基一直奉行「地道式經營」，故餐牌上除了招牌炸雞外，還會推出地道食物，例如內地肯德基會提供油條、粥品、北京雞卷等。據悉，除了開創全國首間「雷鋒精神」主題餐廳外，肯德基還準備在全省開展「雷鋒火種K計劃」，將雷鋒學習活動常態化，讓小朋友藉由故事認識雷鋒、學習雷鋒。<br />\n<br />\n這間雷鋒主題餐廳引起美國《華盛頓郵報》的注意，並刊登了報道。文中形容，美國招牌與中共紅色偶像是個「罕見搭配」（A rare matching of an iconic American brand with Communist propaganda）。<br />\n<br />\n1963年3月，毛澤東呼籲同胞向雷鋒這名因公殉職的23歲青年學習，題詞「向雷鋒同志學習」，並把3月5日定為「學雷鋒紀念日」。雷鋒從此成為家喻戶曉的「共產主義戰士」代表。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190307/59337483\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190307%2F59337483&d=m7n5JD7ZMd19sx07z0x1QBY%2Fip2Wc62AYORpdIbS17M%3D&h=66fdb7d8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190307%2F59337483&h=869a3165\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190307/59337483</a>"},{"pid":"f1e5ac0536885adcfac3c0f0c551d9944b606de7","tid":1050588,"uid":28765,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T03:45:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.aboluowang.com/uploadfile/2013/0319/20130319101251575.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.aboluowang.com%2Fuploadfile%2F2013%2F0319%2F20130319101251575.jpg&h=03b6f01d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4e6f508daddf5e90bbcf89b80cb42ff04002c017","tid":1050588,"uid":177089,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f1e5ac0536885adcfac3c0f0c551d9944b606de7","tid":1050588,"uid":28765,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T03:45:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.aboluowang.com/uploadfile/2013/0319/20130319101251575.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.aboluowang.com%2Fuploadfile%2F2013%2F0319%2F20130319101251575.jpg&h=03b6f01d&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T03:51:48.000Z","msg":"獲毛主席親自接見"},{"pid":"d68b95e97c39bc5a4bf13ed250a9b23e95aa7a64","tid":1050588,"uid":161222,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T14:42:27.000Z","msg":"這是甚麼狗屁餐廳，我的炸雞都點了半天了，怎麼還沒來？<br />\n<br />\n先生，不好意思，您剛點的是共產主義套餐。<br />\n<br />\n媽的，老子不吃了，讓開！<br />\n<br />\n報告領導！又發現一個走資的！這下㕑房有肉了！"},{"pid":"eead243e20fd04e490970df11819983c10ff2c06","tid":1050588,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T14:43:08.000Z","msg":"不如改埋名唔好叫肯德基"}]}